# Arduino Friction Coefficient Measurement System

This project is an Arduino-based device designed to measure friction behavior using sensor data.

## Overview
The system measures distance changes using a sensor.  
When the distance decreases and then returns to the initial value, the program counts the motion cycle.

This allows automated measurement of repeated friction experiments.

## Technologies
- Arduino
- Distance Sensor
- Embedded Systems

## Features
- Sensor-based motion detection
- Automated cycle counting
- Experimental measurement device

